			<h1 class="sm-hero-h1">KNOW YOUR<br>ZONES.<span class="sm-orange">FEEL THE SCIENCE.</span></h1>
			<p class="sm-hero-explainer">Real-time core body temperature. Five physiological zones.</p>
			<p class="sm-hero-sub">Every other sauna app runs a timer. SaunaMind tracks what's actually happening inside your body — in real time.</p>
			<div class="sm-trust">
				<div class="sm-trust-item">Military-validated algorithm</div>
				<div class="sm-trust-item">Bluetooth &middot; Smart Watches &middot; Wearables</div>
				<div class="sm-trust-item">Peer-reviewed science</div>
			</div>
			<div style="margin-top:32px; text-align:center;">
				<a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/saunamind" style="display:inline-block;">
					<img src="/appstore-badge.svg" alt="Download on the App Store" width="180" height="60" style="transition:transform 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='scale(1.05)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='scale(1)'">
